"""
=============================================================================
File: .gitignore
Capabilities:
1. Security: Prevents accidental commits of .env files and JSON keys.
2. Data Privacy: Blocks local data files (CSV, Excel) from entering version control.
3. Cleanliness: Ignores Python cache and virtual environment folders.
=============================================================================
"""

# Security & Environment Variables
.env
credentials.json
token.json
*service_account*.json

# Data Files (Prevent accidental uploads of large/sensitive files)
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.parquet
*.duckdb
*.db

# Python Virtual Environments
venv/
env/
.venv/

# Python Cache
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# OS Generated Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

gcs_service_account.json